{"tid":611190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"箍牙撚入一入黎","createTime":"2018-03-30T17:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T10:54:10.000Z","uid":30612,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6542c417f514be119d79d5389f1297c14dbc1556","tid":611190,"uid":30612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"我個情況係咁樣<br />\n人中個顎骨位偏突<br />\n有d似呢幅圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/011517_4b3a3e1f87dcfb4d43b2e0932e844a91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F011517_4b3a3e1f87dcfb4d43b2e0932e844a91.png&h=5351a182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牙醫建議我脫小叩齒箍牙<br />\n我想要既效果係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/011718_f443679ac8d4f070c6380fcebf4b47c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F011718_f443679ac8d4f070c6380fcebf4b47c8.png&h=2a2995a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無成功既箍牙巴絲好似我咁最後係得到滿意既效果<br />\n我而家最concern係驚箍完發現原來舊顎骨根本推唔到入去<br />\n得d牙向後推  但舊骨就推唔到<br />\n我concept有錯就糾正"},{"pid":"921b2df9b4f395097edda3c45d3df4c041af0b58","tid":611190,"uid":30612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3dd31081d86d9b0cf5c17da6febbac1f348f1e","tid":611190,"uid":30612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f2d368519f78e36991d27a674b887a648ef6de","tid":611190,"uid":30612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"588a53cfbe86a2a476650dca72cb53bfbf72a4f5","tid":611190,"uid":30612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"189c8b99169a34d991b09ba57a14f75a3901bbf5","tid":6111